						<summary>

						<p>The record is very much damaged and dated the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Manmatha, Kārttika, śu. 15.</hi> It mentions the <hi rend="italic">Daḷavāyi</hi> <hi rend="bold">Hampainavaru,</hi> agent to the Mysore king <hi rend="bold">Kaṇṭhīrava-Narasarāja-Vaḍēru.</hi> There is no means of knowing to which of the kings of this name the record belongs.</p>						

